en_225413_0	Muttiah Muralitharan, the former Sri Lankan legendary cricketer states that there is no truth to the reports being published about him on social media.
en_225413_1	Muralitharan made this statement in response to a query from Hiru news regarding the social media reports that he would contest the next general election.
en_225413_2	Muttiah Muralitharan stated that he has never made any statement regarding entering politics.
en_225413_3	He also stated that he categorically rejects all reports stating that he will contest the next general election.
en_225413_4	Muralitharan requested sports fans who love him to stop sharing such false reports on social media.
